Check out Samsung Bespoke AI! https://bit.ly/austinnnotduncanYT
With Bespoke AI, Samsung has an ecosystem of appliances that use real intelligence to save time and money for keeping food fresh, washing (and drying) clothes quickly and even live streaming from your oven.

Retrospekt claims to sell premium refurbished retro tech, but are their $350 typewriters and $380 Polaroids really worth the price? I bought their most popular items to find out if you're paying for quality or just hype. Some surprising discoveries when comparing to prices elsewhere...
